{
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "Stack-detection catalog used by /brain init (Milestone #2). Each entry's signals are evaluated against the user's cwd; if all signals match, the stack is reported as detected. The detected_skill field names the skill that will be auto-installed once Milestone #3 lands the skills/detected/* skills — for M#2, detected stacks are only reported, not installed.",
